# Deployment Standards

## Script Organization
- Use TypeScript for all deployment scripts
- Organize scripts by deployment type
- Use environment variables for configuration
- Implement proper error handling

## Deployment Process
- Verify contracts before deployment
- Use deterministic addresses when needed
- Implement proper access controls
- Include contract verification
- Document deployment addresses

## Network Management
- Use appropriate networks for different stages
- Implement proper gas management
- Handle network-specific configurations
- Use proper account management

## Security
- Never hardcode private keys
- Use environment variables for sensitive data
- Implement proper access controls
- Verify contract ownership

## Documentation
- Document deployment procedures
- Include network-specific instructions
- Document contract addresses
- Include verification steps

## Error Handling
- Implement comprehensive error handling
- Log deployment information
- Handle network failures gracefully
- Provide clear error messages